<i>noun</i>: 자이나교 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>자이나교</dt><br>
<dd>religion founded in the 6th century BC as a revolt against Hinduism; emphasizes asceticism and immortality and transmigration of the soul; denies existence of a perfect or supreme being</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: Jainism</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
